Package de.hsmw.threemaextractor.service.data.contact

Record Class Contact

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
de.hsmw.threemaextractor.service.data.contact.Contact
Record Components:
identity - Threema ID
firstName - first name (specified by user), null if not set
lastName - last name (specified by user), null if not set
nickname - nickname (specified by contact)
androidContactId - ID of associated android contact, null if contact is not saved in Android Contacts app
verificationLevel - contacts trust level

  • 0 - contact is only known by Threema ID
  • 1 - contact is linked to Android Contacts app by phone number or e-mail
  • 2 - id and public key of contact have been manually checked by scanning the contact's QR code
isHidden - contact is hidden in app (requires Android display lock to see)
contactAvatar - avatar of the contact, null if the contact has no avatar or the encrypted file was deleted (see Avatar.getContactAvatarFile(File, String, boolean))
public record Contact(String identity, String firstName, String lastName, String nickname, String androidContactId, int verificationLevel, boolean isHidden, Avatar contactAvatar) extends Record
